  <name>Lyrics</name>
  <summary>The beautiful way to sing your songs</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Lyrics is an application that displays lyrics for songs you are listeningto, it query the song through MPRIS protocol, search, downloads the lyricfile and display it scrolling syncronized.</p>
  </description>
